LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidcut.label: Arachnic acid chewing seeds
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidcut.description: A species of Arachnidium, with low intelligence, usually fired as a living projectile. After hitting an enemy, if it has not yet disintegrated, it continues to bite the enemy with its acid-filled jaws.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidcut.comps.CompMech: From the moment they are born, this special Arachnid worm is on the road to death—its lifespan is so short.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidcut.tools.0.label: giant jaw
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Skyhive.label: Arachne Tensu species
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Skyhive.description: It is a type of Arachne beetle, has low intelligence, and is usually launched like a missile by a master insect. It has the ability to adjust its posture during flight to track its enemies, and after being hit, it clings onto the enemy and continues to bite with its jaws, attacking until its gill spines loosen and fall.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Skyhive.comps.CompMech: From the moment they are born, this special Arachnid worm is on the road to death—its lifespan is so short.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Skyhive.tools.0.label: giant jaw
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidling.label: Arachne explosive species
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidling.description: A type of arachne beetle, it has low intelligence and attacks its enemies with a self-destructive attack. When it gets close to an enemy, it explodes acid sac, creating a dangerous acidic mist.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidling.comps.CompMec: From the moment they are born, this special Arachnid worm is on the road to death—its lifespan is so short.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Acidling.tools.0.label: giant jaw
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Empsuicider.label: Arachne explosive species
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Empsuicider.descriptio: It is a type of Arachne worm that has low intelligence and attacks enemies with a self-destruct attack.When it approaches an enemy, it emits an EMP and stuns the accompanying mechanoid.
LanguageData.ArachnaeBase_Race_Empsuicider.comps.Comp: From the moment they are born, this special Arachnid worm is on the road to death—its lifespan is so short.
